KK Handique University

The KK Handique University is an open and distance education university. This university, which is located in Guwahati, was created in 2005. B.Tech, B.Sc, B.Com, BA, M.Tech, M.Sc, MA, M.Com are among the 2024 admissions options.

KKHSOU is anticipated to launch its application process in the near future. To begin the admission process, the student must go to the KKHSOU Distance Education Admission kk open university‘s official website. KK Handique University offers undergraduate and graduate programmes, and entrance to any undergraduate programme is determined by the results of the previous qualifying examination. UGC-NET scores are used to determine admission to Ph.D. and M.Phil. programmes. Admission to postgraduate programmes is competitive and requires a bachelor’s degree. MBA entrance examinations, such as the MAT, must be passed.

KK Handiqui University DDE Eligibility Criteria:

The KKHSOU Distance Education Admission University provides many courses to the Candidates at both the UG and PG levels; the eligibility criteria for the entry form for entries to the University is as given below:

Candidates who have valid passing 10+2 level exams from any recognized University are eligible to apply for admissions in all UG level courses offered by the KKHSOU Courses Admission University.

The Candidates applying in the course of PG level are to clear off the UG qualification required for them to apply in admission 2024.

Conclusion

Among the top 5 universities in Assam, KK Handique University is the top University which is UGC-DEB as well as NAAC accredited. The students who want to pursue distance education in any of the above mentioned courses, can go for this university without any second thoughts. To know more about the other top universities in Assam, check out our website distanceeducationschool.com.
